<TITLE>
Menominee Language and the Menominee Indian Tribe (Menomini, Menomonie, Mamaceqtaw)
</TITLE>

<META NAME="description" CONTENT="Language, culture, history and genealogy of the Menomini or Menominee tribe. Covers Menominee Indians in Michigan and Wisconsin.">
